{
  "text": "14 Infected humans then transmitted the virus to other humans, likely through close contact with respiratory tract secretions. [CITATION_1] Nipah virus isolates from Malaysia and Bangladesh have been shown to share a sequence identity of 91.8% on the nucleotide level and >92% on the amino acid level.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "2248122"
